clinic.description: Experience top-notch, truly patient-centric dental services any day of the week with flexible scheduling that includes early mornings, late evenings, weekends, and even holidays. Whether you're dealing with an unexpected weekend dental emergency, scheduling a routine wellness check-up, or exploring advanced cosmetic procedures, our talented team is committed to providing personalized care in a welcoming environment. Let's change the way you feel about going to the dentist!

notificationSettings.automatedWelcomeMessageToPatientTemplate: Thank you for submitting an appointment request! We're excited to welcome you to our office. Currently, we are reviewing the details of your request and verifying your insurance coverage. Our office participates with most Aetna, Cigna, Premera, and United Concordia Elite PPO plans, and we also accept many MetLife and Guardian PPO plans as a non-contracted provider. We will notify you about the next steps soon. If you have any questions in the meantime, please don’t hesitate to reach out to us.
